OL,3,CImam who reached out to rioters says
OL,4,C'don't fight fire with fire'
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports correspondent Tim
OL,7,FScott has been speaking to Imam Adam
OL,8,FKelwick ahead of potential riots
OL,9,Facross the UK.
OL,11,FAn Imam at England's oldest mosque who
OL,12,Freached out to rioters is appealing
OL,13,Ffor people to not "fight fire with
OL,14,Ffire", ahead of potential riots across
OL,15,Fthe nation.
OL,17,FAdam Kelwick, an Imam at Abdullah
OL,18,FQuilliam Mosque in Liverpool, crossed
OL,19,Fthe police line on Friday, 2 August,
OL,20,Fto speak to people on the other side.
