OL,3,CImam who reached out to rioters says
OL,4,C'don't fight fire with fire'
OL,6,FViolence broke out in Southport,
OL,7,FLiverpool and Walton in the wake of a
OL,8,Fknife attack which saw three children
OL,9,Fkilled.
OL,11,FMr Kelwick said: "I've spoken to young
OL,12,Fmen in the muslim community and one
OL,13,Fthing I have been saying is that you
OL,14,Fhave to be careful ` this is almost a
OL,15,Ftrap that has been set up for you.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
