OL,3,CImam who reached out to rioters says
OL,4,C'don't fight fire with fire'
OL,6,F"Don't fight fire with fire, don't
OL,7,Ffight violence with violence because
OL,8,Fif you do what they are doing, like
OL,9,Fsmashing up buildings and setting fire
OL,10,Fto things, they will be there waiting
OL,11,Ffor you with their cameras ready.
OL,13,F"They will put you on social media and
OL,14,Fconvince the whole world that you are
OL,15,Fthe problem and that muslims are the
OL,16,Fproblem.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
