OL,3,CImam who reached out to rioters says
OL,4,C'don't fight fire with fire'
OL,6,F"That's what we need to avoid now and
OL,7,Fwe need to de-escalate things and make
OL,8,Fsure that we continue to build bridges
OL,9,Fwhich we have already established with
OL,10,Flots of people in our society."
OL,12,FMerseyside Police has put in place a
OL,13,FSection 60 Order across Liverpool from
OL,14,F1:38pm on Wednesday, 7 August, until
OL,15,F4am on Thursday, 8 August.
OL,17,FThe extension has been introduced to
OL,18,Fprevent incidents of disorder and
OL,19,Fcriminality in light of potential
OL,20,Friots in the city.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
