OL,3,CImam who reached out to rioters says
OL,4,C'don't fight fire with fire'
OL,6,FMr Kelwick continued: "I think
OL,7,Feverybody needs to be extra vigilant
OL,8,Fand extra safe.
OL,10,F"A lot of people have been reaching
OL,11,Fout to me and saying 'how are you able
OL,12,Fto go over to the other side and speak
OL,13,Fto these people and build links with
OL,14,Fthem?'
OL,16,F"I tell them that it is very easy to
OL,17,Fdo because they are just humans like
OL,18,Fwe are, but that is dependent on
OL,19,Fsecurity first and foremost.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
