OL,3,CImam who reached out to rioters says
OL,4,C'don't fight fire with fire'
OL,6,F"Things have to be calm before you can
OL,7,Fmake that step to reach out."
OL,9,FHe added: "I don't just think it's the
OL,10,Fmuslim community that are feeling
OL,11,Funsafe and concerned, but they
OL,12,Fespecially are. But I think everybody
OL,13,Fis."
OL,15,FThe Imam spoke to a leader of a youth
OL,16,Fgroups and summer clubs in Liverpool
OL,17,Fwho said that attendance has fallen
OL,18,Fclose to 20% off the back of the
OL,19,FSouthport stabbings on 29 July.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
