OL,3,CImam who reached out to rioters says
OL,4,C'don't fight fire with fire'
OL,6,F"Everybody is affected right now,
OL,7,Feverybody is on edge, but there are
OL,8,Fspecific situations whereby the muslim
OL,9,Fcommunity is being targeted", he said.
OL,11,F"My my message is very clear. Look
OL,12,Fafter yourselves, stay safe, make sure
OL,13,Fyou security is your first priority
OL,14,Fand after that we can start to carry
OL,15,Fon and come together and unite people."
OL,17,FMore than 400 people have been
OL,18,Farrested so far for involvement in
OL,19,Friots and disorder following the
OL,20,FSouthport attack.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
