OL,6,FPrime Minister Sir Keir Starmer has
OL,7,Fsaid he is expecting "substantive
OL,8,Fsentencing" for those involved.
OL,10,FGreater Manchester Police has asked
OL,11,Fcommunities to "remain calm and to try
OL,12,Fto go about your every-day life".
