OL,3,CImam who reached out to rioters says
OL,4,C'don't fight fire with fire'
OL,6,FIn a statement, GMP said: "We
OL,7,Funderstand the uncertainty and worry
OL,8,Fthat people are feeling about current
OL,9,Ftension, much of which is being
OL,10,Ffuelled by the widespread sharing of
OL,11,Fmisinformation online which is
OL,12,Fsometimes being created with the
OL,13,Fpurpose of creating fear and inciting
OL,14,Fintolerable hate.
OL,16,F"Our advice to communities is to
OL,17,Fremain calm and to try to go about
OL,18,Fyour every-day life.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
