OL,6,F"GMP continues to monitor the
OL,7,Fintelligence to ensure we can respond
OL,8,Feffectively to any incidents of
OL,9,Fdisorder.
OL,11,F"And, if we believe there needs to be
OL,12,Fspecific information about anything
OL,13,Femerging we will tell people and offer
OL,14,Fadvice."
